Key concepts: Needs of life--food, habitat, water, shelter, air, light, minerals.
See LO-III.2 e.4.
Real-world contexts: Selected ecosystems, such as an aquarium, rotting log, terrarium, backyard, local pond or wetland, wood lot.
2.
