Key concepts: Participants and relationships--food chain, food web, energy pyramid, energy flow, producers, consumers, decomposers.
See LO-III.2 m.3 (producers), PCM-IV.2 h.4 (conservation of energy).
Real-world contexts: Energy pyramids for food webs in various ecosystems.
